---
import BaseLayout from '../../../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';

const locale = 'en';
const canonicalUrl = 'https://www.core-attorneys.com/en/privacy/';
const alternateUrl = 'https://www.core-attorneys.com/de/datenschutz/';
const lastUpdated = '4 March 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | CORE Attorneys"
  description="Privacy policy of CORE Attorneys AG under Swiss data protection law (DSG) and GDPR."
  locale={locale}
  canonicalUrl={canonicalUrl}
  alternateUrl={alternateUrl}
  noindex={false}
>
  <div class="py-12 bg-bg-light border-b border-bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-4">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-sans text-text/50 list-none m-0 p-0">
          <li><a href="/en/" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Home</a></li>
          <li aria-hidden="true" class="text-text/30">/</li>
          <li class="text-text" aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-text" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm text-text/50 mt-3">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <article class="py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:text-text prose-a:text-accent">

        <h2>1. Controller</h2>
        <p>
          The controller responsible for data processing on this website is:<br />
          CORE Attorneys AG, Dufourstrasse 105, CH-8008 Zurich, Switzerland<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@core-attorneys.com">info@core-attorneys.com</a>
        </p>

        <h2>2. Principles</h2>
        <p>
          CORE Attorneys AG processes personal data in accordance with Swiss data protection law (DSG) and, where applicable, the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). We only process data that is necessary for the respective purpose.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Cookies and tracking</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses <strong>no cookies</strong> and no personal tracking. No tracking pixels, social media cookies or Google Analytics are used.
        </p>
        <p>
          We use Cloudflare Web Analytics for aggregated, anonymised statistics on website usage. This solution is cookie-free and does not collect personal data.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Hosting and infrastructure</h2>
        <p>
          This website is hosted via Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare processes server logs and technical connection data (including IP addresses) as part of providing the service. More information: <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Contact by email</h2>
        <p>
          If you contact us by email, your details will be stored to process your enquiry. This data will not be passed on to third parties and will be deleted after processing is complete, unless statutory retention obligations apply.
        </p>

        <h2>6. LinkedIn</h2>
        <p>
          This website embeds a LinkedIn feed via the Walls.io service. This is only loaded when you actively give your consent. When loaded, data is transmitted to Walls.io (Walls.io GmbH) and LinkedIn (LinkedIn Corporation, USA). More information: <a href="https://walls.io/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Walls.io Privacy</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Maps (OpenStreetMap)</h2>
        <p>
          The contact page includes an option to load a map via OpenStreetMap. This is only loaded after your active consent. When loaded, data is transmitted to OpenStreetMap (OpenStreetMap Foundation, UK). More information: <a href="https://wiki.osmfoundation.org/wiki/Privacy_Policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OpenStreetMap Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Fonts</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses self-hosted fonts. No fonts are loaded from Google Fonts or other external services.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to access, rectify, erase and restrict the processing of your personal data, as well as the right to data portability. Please contact: <a href="mailto:info@core-attorneys.com">info@core-attorneys.com</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Changes</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to update this privacy policy at any time. The current version is always available on this page.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
